Interpretability is the science of answering one question:

Why did this system produce this output?

For humans, animals, AI models, organizations, and even evolution, interpretability is about making hidden internal processes observable.

For Pantheon, I think it becomes much broader than “AI interpretability.” It becomes the science of recovering latent structure from observable behavior.

